The paper discusses a defense mechanism for adversarial attacks on machine learning models, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV) to evaluate the effectiveness of the defense mechanism. Additionally, the paper discusses the implementation of the defense mechanism in software engineering (cs.SE) applications.
